en.cancel: Goodbye, please tell your friends about humanbios!
en.choose_lang: Please select the language you want to me to talk in to you from now on.
en.location: Can you send us your location so we can track potential spread or warn you about cases close to you?
en.story:
Hello! Thank you for contacting Human Bios. Before we ask you a couple of self-diagnosis questions, take the opportunity to tell us your story, if you would like to.

Where are you right now? How are your friends, your family? Do you feel safe?
en.story_too_long: Sorry, the maximum on characters we allow for your story are 400, try to keep it a bit shorter :)
en.selfie: You can also take a picture of yourself right now and send it here. This will help other people to understand your situation.
en.disclaimer:
With your consent, we will store and analyze your use of the HumanBios App for scientific research and to improve your experience when using the HumanBios App. 

If you give your consent, we will contact you over the medium where you gave your permission for scientific research and to improve your experience when using the Human Bios App.

For further information, visit the privacy policy at https://bit.ly/HumanBios_privacy_note.

If you have read and give your consent to the Privacy Note press 'accept'.
en.are_you_okay: This is an emergency service. Do you need help?
en.medical: Are you looking for medical assistance? If you would just like to talk to someone press no.
en.stressed: Okay. Are you feeling stressed or anxious?
en.wanna_help: Glad to hear. Would you like to help others?
en.mental: Please tell us a little about your current situation. How are you feeling? Are you afraid? Take a minute to relax and breath. Tell us also about your friends and family
en.helping: Welcome new member. We are so glad you’re here! Please provide a short description of what you would like to help with and what you can do. Keep it brief and professional
en.bye: Okay, please tell your friends about humanbios!
en.coughing: Could you send us a video or voice note of you coughing? This will help us to understand your situation and provide you with better information.
en.coughing_wrong_answer: We sorry, this is not a supported media type. Please try sending a voice note/message or a video recording.
en.qa_intro: This bot will ask a series of question now which will help understanding your case. First one:
en.qa_error: I am sorry, you need to press one of the buttons.
en.qa_multi: Since this is a multiple choice question, please press more options if you want to. Otherwise, press {0}
en.forward_doctor: We have forwarded your request and come back to you as soon as possible.
en.forward_shrink: We have forwarded your request and come back to you as soon as possible.
en.forward_member: We have forwarded your request and come back to you as soon as possible.
en.invalid_answer: Sorry, but that's not any of the expected answers.
en.found: Hey, we found a doctor who can help you. You are now connected to them - simply send your messages in here.
en.forbidden: Sorry, I can't handle that type of messages!

Wenn Sie Ihre Zustimmung geben, werden wir Sie über das Medium kontaktieren, in dem Sie Ihre Erlaubnis für wissenschaftliche Forschung erteilt haben, und um Ihre Erfahrungen mit der Verwendung der Human Bios App zu verbessern.

de.forward_shrink: Wir haben Ihre Anfrage weitergeleitet und werden uns so schnell wie möglich bei Ihnen melden.

ru.selfie: Вы также можете сфотографировать себя прямо сейчас и отправить его сюда. Это поможет другим людям понять вашу ситуацию.
